node.title: Man seen chasing girl and dog, police seek witnesses
node.content: ["Police investigating an incident in which a man reportedly chased a girl and her dog want to speak to those who came to her assistance.", "It happened at about 7:30pm on Monday on North St in Feilding, near the intersection with Denbigh St, police said.\u00a0", "\"Police are aware of a number of people who assisted the girl and her mother at the time of the incident,\" they said on Friday afternoon.", "\"Police are particularly interested in speaking with two people out jogging, as well as a passing motorist driving a white sedan who pulled over to help the victims.", "\"We would also like to speak with anyone else who witnessed this incident or anyone with information that may assist our enquiries.\"", "Anyone who knows anything about the incident is urged to call police on 105, quoting file number 211214/8715, or Crime Stoppers on 0800 555 111."]
